Package: compassutils
Title: Utilities for working with compass and map bearings
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2024-03-26
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Bedward", , "michael.bedward@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9986-1286"))
Description: Provides some simple functions for working with map compass bearings
    and converting between compass angles (0 is north, 90 is east etc.) and 
    Cartesian angles (0 is east, 90 is north etc.) as used by R's trigonometric 
    functions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
